Class ConjuntUsuaris

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
java.util.AbstractList<E>
java.util.ArrayList<Usuari>
src.recomanador.domini.ConjuntUsuaris
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<Usuari>, Collection<Usuari>, List<Usuari>, RandomAccess
public class ConjuntUsuaris extends ArrayList<Usuari>
This class describes a set of users as a extension of a users ArrayList. It keeps the elements ordered by the id of users, to achieve a better performance when asking for a user with a certain ID.
